Blastomussa wellsi

— 
Wijsman-Best, 1973
: figs. 1–2; Chevalier: 1975, pl. XXIX, fig. 5, pl. XXXI, figs. 3–5; 
Head, 1978
: fig. 1b; 
Veron & Pichon, 1980
: figs. 395 and 769; 
Scheer & Pillai, 1983
: pl. 35 figs. 7–8, 10–11; 
Veron, 1986
: figs. 1, 3, 4; 
Veron, 2000
: Volume 3, pp. 6–7, figs. 1–3, 6; 
Hoeksema & van Ofwegen, 2004
; 
