Polyp tentacles retracted towards the oral disc during the day (
Figs. 8D
, 
9D
). Mantle vesicles rugged and sometimes of lighter colour (
Fig. 9D
), polyp colours ranging from light brown, or orange to bright red, and sometimes with green orals discs (
Fig. 8D
).
